:: Lap-ride-Dialogue [nobr]

<<if $sex.position =="Lap ride">>
    <<if $sex.role =="Top">>
        _n.name sits on your lap, looking at you.
    <<elseif $sex.role == "Bottom">>
        You sit on _n.name's lap, looking at them.
    <</if>>
<<elseif $sex.position =="Reverse Lap ride">>
    <<if $sex.role =="Top">>
        _n.name sits on your lap, facing away from you.
    <<elseif $sex.role == "Bottom">>
        You sit on _n.name's lap, facing away from them.
    <</if>>

<</if>>